IT’S FINALLY HERE! My first Modeling workshop in collaboration with @cairophotoweek @photopiacairostudio 
Registration link in my bio 🙌🏻💖
————————————-

Sherouk Farid Modeling House
Striking poses and making impact; discover how to be a supermodel!
A two day Workshop, A guide to fashion industry and modeling.
What you will learn?
- Dynamic posing. 
- Branding yourself. 
- Dealing with agencies.
-  Signature runway walks. 
- Keys to networking.
-  Expectations vs. reality.
Day 1
• Introduction.
• Discussion about fashion and modeling.
• Live photoshoot.
• Directions in building portfolio.
• How to’s.
• Q&A’s with experienced creatives in the fashion industry.
Day 2
• Application and practical demonstration.
• Polaroid shots for each model.
*The workshop is suitable for aspiring models, new faces who have the dream and ambition to learn on an international level and become the next face of Egypt.
Registration link: https://forms.gle/UCNLySDw7Mgpwrag7
 
Dates: 17th and 18th February from 10 to 3pm
Location: Downtown Cairo, Consoleya Co-working Space.
 Maximum number of participants: 20
Duration: 2 days.
